2011-08-24T05:22:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-24/iran-expects-to-find-four-new-gas-fields-mehr-reports.html
Iran  expects to find four new gas
fields before the end of March 2012 following exploration now
being carried out, the state-run  Mehr  news agency said, citing
National Iranian Oil Co.â€™s director for exploration, Mahmoud Mohaddes.  Iran recently discovered the Menar natural gas field
located east of the southern port town of Assaluyeh, according
to the Mehr report. The field holds 17.470 trillion cubic feet
or 495 billion cubic meters of gas and some three fourth of it
is recoverable, the report said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
